{
  "id": "642a36b43c20b6001b30c978",
  "title": "ユニバーサル・ベーシック・インカム",
  "created": 1680488118,
  "updated": 1680491005,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "642a36b3aff09e000029e7a1",
      "text": "ユニバーサル・ベーシック・インカム",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680488118,
      "updated": 1680490882
    },
    {
      "id": "642a3a45aff09e00003b19f2",
      "text": "[https://ssir-j.org/universal_basic_income/ ユニバーサル・ベーシック・インカムはアジアに幸福をもたらす鍵か | スタンフォード・ソーシャルイノベーション・レビュー 日本版]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680489029,
      "updated": 1680489032
    },
    {
      "id": "642a3a48aff09e00003b19f3",
      "text": "自分の中で整理しようとしたけどまだ整理しきれてない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680489032,
      "updated": 1680491005
    },
    {
      "id": "642a41efaff09e0000d93ff2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680490992,
      "updated": 1680490992
    },
    {
      "id": "642a41f0aff09e0000d93ff3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680490992,
      "updated": 1680490992
    },
    {
      "id": "642a36b3aff09e000029e7a2",
      "text": " 日本の大学生が「[好きなことを仕事にする]」ディスカッションを企画",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680488118,
      "updated": 1680489071
    },
    {
      "id": "642a36b3aff09e000029e7a3",
      "text": "\t 卒業後の「[社畜]」化を懸念",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680488118,
      "updated": 1680489077
    },
    {
      "id": "642a36b3aff09e000029e7a4",
      "text": "\t AI技術の進化により、[反復的な仕事]が取って代わられる可能性",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680488118,
      "updated": 1680489078
    },
    {
      "id": "642a36b3aff09e000029e7a5",
      "text": "\t [ユニバーサル・ベーシック・インカム]([UBI])の[所得保障]としての可能性",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680488118,
      "updated": 1680489111
    },
    {
      "id": "642a36b3aff09e000029e7a6",
      "text": " ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680488118,
      "updated": 1680489191
    },
    {
      "id": "642a3ae7aff09e00003b19f4",
      "text": " 韓国で支持",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680489191,
      "updated": 1680489209
    },
    {
      "id": "642a3b0eaff09e00003b19f8",
      "text": " \t[イ・ウォンジェ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680489231,
      "updated": 1680489231
    },
    {
      "id": "642a3b10aff09e00003b19f9",
      "text": " \t\t[ラボ2050]の創設者",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680489232,
      "updated": 1680489242
    },
    {
      "id": "642a3af8aff09e00003b19f7",
      "text": "\t 新政党「[時代転換]」がUBIや社会イノベーションを推進。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680489209,
      "updated": 1680489756
    },
    {
      "id": "642a3d68aff09e00006e03e6",
      "text": "\t 京畿道（キョンギド）の実験",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680489833,
      "updated": 1680489838
    },
    {
      "id": "642a3b63aff09e00003b19fa",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680489315,
      "updated": 1680489315
    },
    {
      "id": "642a36b3aff09e000029e7a9",
      "text": " 韓国の労働観には「[働かざる者食うべからず]」の考えがある。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680488118,
      "updated": 1680488165
    },
    {
      "id": "642a3b65aff09e00003b19fb",
      "text": "\t\t[自助努力]で生計を立てなければならないと説く[儒教]の影響",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680489317,
      "updated": 1680489325
    },
    {
      "id": "642a3b98aff09e00003b19fe",
      "text": "\t韓国社会の深刻な貧富格差と社会階級の固定化",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680489369,
      "updated": 1680489369
    },
    {
      "id": "642a3b6caff09e00003b19fc",
      "text": "\t\tアカデミー賞を受賞した映画『[パラサイト 半地下の家族]』",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680489325,
      "updated": 1680489369
    },
    {
      "id": "642a3b8aaff09e00003b19fd",
      "text": "\t\t\t暗くじめじめした[半地下]に住み、資格や学歴を詐称することでしか運命を切り開く希望を見いだせない家族の物語",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680489354,
      "updated": 1680489379
    },
    {
      "id": "642a3ba3aff09e00003b19ff",
      "text": "\t[スプーン階級論]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680489379,
      "updated": 1680489402
    },
    {
      "id": "642a3bb9aff09e00003b1a01",
      "text": "\t\t2015年から流行",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680489402,
      "updated": 1680489405
    },
    {
      "id": "642a3db5aff09e00006e03e7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680489909,
      "updated": 1680489909
    },
    {
      "id": "642a3db6aff09e00006e03e8",
      "text": "\t75％以上の回答者が子供の成功に親のコネや財力が必要だと回答",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680489911,
      "updated": 1680489912
    },
    {
      "id": "642a3db6aff09e00006e03e9",
      "text": "\t自営業者が労働者の25.1％を占め、多くが不安定な仕事に従事",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680489911,
      "updated": 1680489913
    },
    {
      "id": "642a3db6aff09e00006e03ea",
      "text": "\t\t従来の雇用関係がなく、社会保障が受けられない制度的問題",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680489911,
      "updated": 1680489915
    },
    {
      "id": "642a3db6aff09e00006e03eb",
      "text": "\t\t失業保険給付金が受給資格のない若者",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680489911,
      "updated": 1680489921
    },
    {
      "id": "642a3dc0aff09e00006e03ec",
      "text": "\t\t30歳未満の10人に1人が失業",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680489921,
      "updated": 1680489921
    },
    {
      "id": "642a3dc4aff09e00006e03ed",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680489924,
      "updated": 1680489924
    },
    {
      "id": "642a3bbdaff09e00003b1a02",
      "text": " 貧富格差と社会階級の固定化が、UBI支持の背景にある。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680489405,
      "updated": 1680489924
    },
    {
      "id": "642a36e4aff09e000029e7ac",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680488167,
      "updated": 1680488167
    },
    {
      "id": "642a3e3daff09e00006e03ee",
      "text": "\t京畿道：韓国で最も人口の多い行政区、人口1200万人",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680490046,
      "updated": 1680490048
    },
    {
      "id": "642a3e3eaff09e00006e03ef",
      "text": "\t24歳向けベーシック・インカム・プログラム開始",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680490046,
      "updated": 1680490063
    },
    {
      "id": "642a3e3eaff09e00006e03f0",
      "text": "\t対象者：17万5000人、3カ月ごとに220ドル相当の[地域通貨]支給",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680490046,
      "updated": 1680490072
    },
    {
      "id": "642a3e3eaff09e00006e03f1",
      "text": "\t若者と中小企業に支持、勤労意欲低下は見られず幸福度上昇",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680490046,
      "updated": 1680490269
    },
    {
      "id": "642a3e3eaff09e00006e03f2",
      "text": "\tソウルの若者：1回限りの就職活動助成金2500ドル相当",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680490046,
      "updated": 1680490269
    },
    {
      "id": "642a3e3eaff09e00006e03f3",
      "text": "\t新型コロナ下：全世帯に1回限り800ドル相当の支援金",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680490046,
      "updated": 1680490270
    },
    {
      "id": "642a3e3eaff09e00006e03f4",
      "text": "\tUBI支持：韓国国民の半数近く",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680490046,
      "updated": 1680490273
    },
    {
      "id": "642a3e3eaff09e00006e03f5",
      "text": "\tイ・ジェミョン：全国民に年間50万ウォン（約430ドル）の基本所得提案、財源は税強化",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680490046,
      "updated": 1680490271
    },
    {
      "id": "642a3f22aff09e00006e03f6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680490274,
      "updated": 1680490274
    },
    {
      "id": "642a3f22aff09e00006e03f7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680490274,
      "updated": 1680490274
    }
  ]
}